abstract: Tunisian Interior Min Najem Gharsalli says security forces have killed three leaders of insurgent group Oqba Ibn Nafa who were attempting to set up base in south of country.
lead_paragraph: Tunisia’s interior minister said the men, who belonged to the group Oqba Ibn Nafa, were trying to establish an armed presence in the south of the country.

headline.main: Tunisian Forces Kill 3 Senior Leaders of Insurgent Group
headline.print_headline: Africa; Tunisia: Three Insurgent Leaders Are Killed
